{"tid":992960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇嚟有班人仲未明白高登用支那CDN／Backend嘅問題","createTime":"2019-01-23T14:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T19:58:38.000Z","uid":11598,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd26aeaa36bdb285cf5a1793943ac5e6012e6ad","tid":992960,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"當年Github 比支那DDOS 就係因為有人係百度統計嘅frontend javascript入邊加料<br />\n偽裝做正常js，入邊加咗段每兩秒就瀏覽某個 github repo嘅code<br />\n而呢啲Analytics 好撚多人用，所以好撚多人都變咗支共嘅殭屍機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n詳情可以自己Google 百度 Github DDOS<br />\n<br />\n唔該自己諗吓高登用阿里雲又好 QQ CDN又好乜都好，後邊有啲咩影響<br />\n唔知佢哋個DB擺邊，如果咁唔好彩真係擺阿里雲嘅話真係send 資料上中共喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前高登個DB就plain text儲password嘅 唔知而家有冇改到呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad4ad4a613bf802e050a0f03a58508e1eaf0c28","tid":992960,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8191094ab94af0849005213f56b1afb7c33f010","tid":992960,"uid":76715,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:32:02.000Z","msg":"有冇飲過東江水都講得出<br />\n好難期望佢地會諗得咁深入<br />\n對高登死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7297181c0e538a282d058f97a1b59900c812e7e","tid":992960,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:34:05.000Z","msg":"點睇有連燈仔認為css framework hack到人機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/992964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/992964</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n巴士入去講兩句"},{"pid":"9aabb08aa78698215dc09fce27873f502b0b2fb0","tid":992960,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7297181c0e538a282d058f97a1b59900c812e7e","tid":992960,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:34:05.0