14:49:04.000Z","msg":"Ant design 彩蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:51:51.000Z","msg":"支那企業級「Ant-design」Library 觸發聖誕彩蛋，俾人屌到仆街<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/955964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/955964</a><br />\n<br />\n柒事重溫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:20:42.000Z","msg":"呢個故事教訓所有既developer,唔好以為open source既野係一定好撚安全<br />\n<br />\n雖然open source個practice可以比close source更有效防範俾人亂咁加d唔應該有既code入去, 但如果無嚴格執行code review有時會做成非常嚴重既後果,e.g. Ant Design彩蛋<br />\n<br />\n由於呢d大型package係由好specific既專業人士去打出來, 用家係信左個code review制度唔會專登放d有問題料入去, 點知支那人hea到做top frontend framework都唔做好呢d practice, 可想而知close source既軟件問題係更為嚴重<br />\n<br />\nbtw Ant Design開發廠係螞蟻金服,即係中國信用系統果個開發者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8dc5d7efb2e9475777a756b02513478971bf28","tid":992960,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d7297181c0e538a282d058f97a1b59900c812e7e","tid":992960,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:34:05.000Z","msg":"點睇有連燈仔認為css framework hack到人機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/992964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/992964</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n巴士入去講兩句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"都話csp同integrity attr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你一開始已經輸左比我"},{"pid":"3010c1456ea97de22a1156621eb9c902ce2dfb4b","tid":992960,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d413bea46d04c48605b3e9c4edf8e33e30db507","tid":992960,"uid":12599,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"50bb042fdef26d5dff2c9c463f7e17732e66f82b","tid":992960,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":